body:
## Steps to reproduce the issue

bug2.sv
```
package in_types_pkg;
typedef struct packed
{
    logic unsigned  [1:0]  m_v;
} in_struct_t;
endpackage

package out_types_pkg;
typedef struct packed
{
    logic unsigned  [1:0]  m_v;
} out_struct_t;
endpackage


function automatic out_types_pkg::out_struct_t e_s (
    input in_types_pkg::in_struct_t din
);
    out_types_pkg::out_struct_t dout;
    dout.m_v = din.m_v;
    return dout;
endfunction
```
`read_verilog -sv bug2.sv`
## Expected behavior

Read wo error.
## Actual behavior

bug2.sv:16: ERROR: syntax error, unexpected TOK_PKG_USER_TYPE

